Sɣur [[Wp/kab/Essaid At Maamar|'''Essaid At Maamar''']]


Yella yiwen wergaz yezmer ad yini fell-as wemdan, wagi d tidett d yiwen. Ass-mi yesla s tmacahutt-nni n winna iḍargen tala, ira ad iɛaned ɣur-s akken a d-slen yes-s medden ula d netta ɣas ma di texnasin, acku d awezɣi yesla yella win neɣ tella tin i d-yuddren ulamma yiwet n tikkelt isem-is ama yelha neɣ dir-it. Akken yewweḍ ɣer tala teqquṛ tɛebbuṭ-is, ur yezmir ara ad yeẓmi tamment-is, ihi yeqqim kann akken yisem-is yemḍel ddaw wakal, yeɣli ssenğaq-is.

Ulac akk amdan yecfan yemlal-d kra n wass tmeṭṭut n yiwen-agi war tadist.Asali uɛebbuḍ ɣur-sen am weskar n tkeṛṛust: „ Mmdel allen-ik ay amdan! Bren tasarut! Lldi allen-ik! Yekker zzhir”.

Netta yiwen-agi mačči d tineslemt i t-yeğğan  yessefrụṛux war tilisa neɣ d axxam i ira a t-yeččaṛ d dderya, acku iḥemmel ayagi neɣ dacu, ala. Ira ad yesfeḍ tilin n uwezɣi akken a d-addren medden isem-is. Diɣ netta seg mi yessaweḍ rrebg ɣer tagust, yessebruruḍ irennu, uɣalen yemdanen ttadren-d isem-is, maca ulac win neɣ tin i iheddṛen fell-as awal aziḍan, ḥala rregmat i yessawalen deffir weɛrur-is.

Argaz tewqeɛ deg-s tmellat, yerra-tt i truẓi uqeṛṛu, yessefk ad yaweḍ asirem-is, ad mmeslayen fell-as medden ayen yelhan. Dacu i s-d-yurew useqdec n wallaɣ-is? At zik qqaṛen: “ Rrbeḥ ur tezriḍ ansi, ur tezriḍ melmi a d-yas“, qqaṛen daɣen: “ Ma yebɣu zzheṛ-ik a d-yerzu fell-ak, a k-yini ṛebbi: Ṭṭef ihi i k-in-yettḥazen!”.

Ula d yiwen-agi d anamek n inzan-agi i d-yerzan fell-as, tekcem-as-d yiwet n tekti s amelɣiɣ-is, din din yessemlal-d arraw-is s umata tikket tamezwarut, yenna-yasen: Azekka ɣas ssirdet udemawen-nwen! “Yerna yesfeḍ-as i yiwen deg-sen imiren axlul s tecdaṭ n ubeṛnus-is”.

Arrac: Ilmend n wacu yessefk ad iriden wudmawen-nneɣ?

Dacu yedṛan ɛni a baba?

Tazwara ira a sen-yuqem tamuffirt, maca nutni ggumman ad brun i wawal, ṛzan-as aqeṛṛu-is s yesteqsiyen-nsen, yuɣal yenna-yasen: Azekkayen d ssuq, dda Bussaɛd n at Nnger nekra-t, nekra-t akken a nawi izgaren di tkamyunt-is, meqqaṛ ad teddum ula d kunwi ma yeggra-d ɣer deffir wemḍiq, ad tekksem lxiq.

ɣas akken arraw-is ur kcimen ara aɣerbaz ( lakul ), ur ɣrin ara yakk taɛṛabt, maca akken d-yeffeɣ wawal-agi n yinig ɣer ssuq seg imi n baba-tsen, zeḍmen fell-as akken ma llan, ḥebbant, ssudnent rnan cnan-as-d tizlitt-nni n “ Ṭalaɛa lbeddṛu ɛalayna”, mlalen “lmuhağiṛin” d “elansaṛ”.

Rnan sin wuḍan-nni war taguni i ten-sɛeddan, ma yeggan bururu, nutni xaṭi. Azekkayen yewweḍ-d dda Bussaɛd n at Nnger ɣer zdat wexxam, yessekr-d yakk adrum s usiwel d ujijjeq n tnaqust n tkeṛṛust( aṣuni ).

Yiwen-nni yelha-d d yezgaren, yessuli-ten wa deffir wayeḍ ɣer tkamyunt, akken iwala yegra-d wemḍiq, yenna-yasen i warraw-is: Tezṛam a tarwa, iqiṭunen-inna n giguẓ nesɛa ɣef tencirt meṛṛa ččuṛen. Ad awen-fkeɣ mraw ( 10 ) n tesdatin ( dqayeq ), win ur d-nettawi ara seg igenni neɣ si tɣerɣeṛt aqiṭun-is i iriran, tebra yemma-s ma yuli-tt! Ur ilaq ara a s-nedṛeg takamyunt i wergaz.

Dda Bussaɛd ihuz aqeṛṛuy-is, am akken ira a s-yini neɣ yenna-yas s usenɛet-nni, d tidet a mmi, kečč trebbaḍ arraw-ik! Dacu kan awal-agi ur d-yeffiɣ ara deg imi-s, ihi yiwen-agi ngum yewwiḍ asirem-is, werɛad slan imeẓẓuɣen-is yemmeslay fell-as wemdan ayen yelhan, maca d tikli, acku dagi isawem-it...

Arrac ikcem-iten lḥir, serrḥen s tazla s iqubac “ iɛfiren”, ččuṛend turin-nsen akken yessefk ngum tuffɣa n yiṭij d rriḥa tasemmamt.

Lewhi n tẓa ( 9 ) n tesdatin uɣalen-d akk glan-d yid-sen  s iqiṭunen ḥala yiwen gar-asen i d-yewwin alibuḍ.

Akken iwala baba-s alibuḍ-nni ger ifassen-is, yenna-yas: A k-rnuɣ kra n tesdatin, lemmer ur d-ttawiḍ ara la droite (ayeffus), yeğğa-k umitṛu ( tamacint)!

Tenṭeq-d tmeṭṭut-is kan akka s leḥkaṛ, acku nettat ur tezmir ara i leɛyaḍ, m´ulac a s-d-teɣli tadist, tenna-yas : Ur ḥwağen ara yakk iqiṭunen neɣ ayen nniḍen, ulac akk dacu a d-rren, sin wussan d sin wuḍan ur ččin ara ula d yiwet n telqimt n weɣrum.

Yiwen : Aha erreẓ akka s yinna, m´ur tebɣiḍ ara ad rẓeɣ amgerḍ-im s tɛekkazt-agi ! Kemm tettḥebbireḍ kan ɣef warraw-im, i lemmer ad beccen yezgaren takamyunt n wergaz!!!

ɣas akken isawem-it tikkelt nniḍen, maca ur t-yesnemmer ara dda Bussaɛd, yečča sakin times deg ul-is.

Akken yessuli argam di tmeṭṭut, iɛedda-d lkuṛṭaj n teslit, yessuli arraw-is s uɣiwel s izgaren, yeldi-d tawwurt n zdat, yeṭṭef taɛekkazt-is ger netta d ucifuṛ, yenna-yas :

Ddimaṛi a dda Bu, ddimaṛi!

Tebɛen zzedwa-nni n teslit, mmi-s-nni yuɣal-d yewwid yid-s ayeffus, maca iseffeṛ-as wewtul.

Deg webrid yekker-itt hetwir, yeqqaṛ-as yiwen-nni i dadda-s Bu: Kksiliṛi, kksiliṛi a dda Bu, err-as m´ulac “poids mort”, a neddubli mmi-s n leḥṛam-inna!

Dda Bussaɛd yessɛedday “les vitesses” s ufus-is ayeffus, netta yesɛadday-itent s tɛekkazt s ufus-is azelmaḍ.

Arrac-nni deffir ṛwan zhu akken iwata rnan dduklen-asen lfuṛuḥ akken yeqqaṛ yiwen.

Deg yiwet n tikkelt ufan-d iman-nsen ger tmeɣra, lkuṛṭaj n teslit, iḍebbalen, rrekban n tkamyunt, tiɣratin, abrid ɣer ssuq war ma yettu wemdan izgaren “ Aɣrum, acriḥ, aqenduṛ si Xincla”.

Wwḍen ɣer wanda msebḍan iberdan, mgaraden abrid uɣen nutni d teslit.

Akken ssawḍen ɣer ssuq, rsen-d am nutni am yezgaren, kecmen akken ɣer ṛṛehba.Yiwen wergaz n taddart-nsen yettẓalla, yezwar-iten mi yewweḍ ɣer ssuq. Ameẓẓallu-agi yezga yeččufu i lɣaci aqenduṛ, d tagi i d tafellaḥt-is.Win ira a t-ikellex, a s-iwet kra n tsegnatin s lehduṛ, sakin a t-yer am ssaɛa yeqqen deg ufus-is, s anda i s-yehwa a t-yawi neɣ a t-yerr.

Maca yiwen-nni ulac melmi i s-icuf aqenduṛ, acku ulac akk deg wacu i t-yeḥwağ yerna yenna-yas i wul-is, fiḥel ma wwiɣ ddnub n lkasaṛna-inna n warraw-is. Ameẓẓalu-agi yal ssuq d netta i d amezwaru ɣur-s. Dacu yettgabaṛ wemcum?

Yettlus aqenduṛ d acebḥan am winna n Joseph Ratzinger ( Benoît XVI ), ireffed-it-id  seg tecdaṭ-nni n zdat seg idaṛṛen ḥala ma d ddaw temgerṭ-is, yettadam nnig wayen i wumi zemren yecwariyen n izembyal n yeɣyal di sin.Widak akk yeznuzun di ssuq wa yessen-it, wa yetteddu a t-yissin. Iles-is ziḍ am tamment, yettmeslay s yisem n nnbi d ṣṣuḥaba, ladɣa ttqadaṛen-t akken llan. Ansi iɛedda ad yeččaṛ afus-is s wayen a yessiweḍ s iciwi-s, da ad yeddem semmus ( 5 ) n tfirsin, da d arḍel n lmeɛjun, dahi d taqeṛɛett n uberyanti...atg. Mi teččuṛ telwaḥt-nni yettaken anzi ɣer tin n ubilduziṛ mar a tali, ad iɛeddi yakk fell-asen, yeqqaṛ-asen ğğiɣ-ken di sslama n ṛebbi, ihi ar ssuq d-iteddun ma yekteb uxellaq „ ɛezza wa ğella“!

Ass-nni wissen dacu n wugur i t-yewten, ifaq-as yiwen seg widak-nni yeznuzun di ssuq, netta argaz-nni d yiwen i d-asen-yessnen i at ddemyaṭi-agi, iwala-t mi yettɛemmiṛ tijujtin, yeğğa-t akken d-yelha yettarra ṣṣerf i yiwen wemɣar, yessenser idaṛṛen-is.

Yessaked kan umeẓẓallu-nni ɣer deffir-s, yufa yedfeṛ-d wergaz-nni leɛqab-is yerna s tazla. Iɣawel isurrifen-is, yurar-itt amzun iḥar kan, acku yugad a tt-yesfiq ɣef yiman-is.

Akken yeffeɣ si ssuq, yekcem ɣer ṛṛeḥba n yezgaren, yuɣal yetteddu kan s ttawil, ur yugad ara yakk sakin a t-id-yelḥeq wergaz-nni seg wakken yeɛqel-it d amuḥṛic, yeẓra yessefk ad yili wemdan am winna ɣur-s isalli llan ataṣ n imeẓẓulla yellan am netta di ssuq.

Lemmer a d-yeğğ tagnitt kan tamecṭituḥt sselɛa-s, ad tedṛu yid-s am win yetteklen ɣef wemcic ad as-iɛas turin. Akken yessuli leḥsab-is i teffeɣ, argaz-nni yuɣal s amḍiq-is. ɣas ma akukru yeffeɣ seg ul n umeẓẓallu, maca icekkaben-is ttergigin. Yessaweḍ-it sidi-s ɛebdelqadeṛ Ğilali almi d zdat yiwen-nni n taddart-is d warraw-is yellan di ṛṛeḥba, teɣli-yas yakk sselɛa-nni i d-yuker si tergigit-nni yugaren tin n tkekkuct. Lemmer teqqim sselɛa-nni tuzzar kra n tegnitt tamecṭuḥt di tɣerɣeṛt, talli imiren a tt-rren yezgaren d rmim.

Seg wakken isuɣ weɣyul di lebḥer, yezlem yiwen-nni yiwet n tkebbanit kan seg ubaṭayu-nni yesɛa, zeḍmen ɣef lerbaḥ-nni yeɣlin, din din rran tiɣawsiwin s imeḍqan-nsnen, tissegnit mačči teqqim tuzzar, am akken ssulin-as i umeẓẓallu aɛebbuḍ am win yessalay baba-tsen i yemma-tsen, yeddem tadist n sselɛa.

Akken tɛedda tegnitt-nni, tebṛeq deg igenni, tezlez tmurt akka acemma, yessawel rrɛud, smermɣen yakk yezgaren, beccen yeɣyal ɣef yiwet n tikkelt, terwi, tebberwi. Acuɣer?

Yewweḍ-d lawan ideg yesla yiwen-nni yemmeslay fell-as wemdan ameslay yesnecṛaḥen ul-is, yenna-yasen umeẓẓallu-nni i warraw-is: Umedra! Umedra! Ad yeḥrez ṛebbi baba-twen i ken-id-yessufɣen d imuḥṛicen! Tettuṛebbam yerna d tidett a tarwa!

ɣlin-as-d imeṭṭawen si tmendit i yiwen yerna seg imiren ur yeqqim ara d yiwen kan, yuɣal d mraw ( 10 ). Yegray-as-d yiwen wezger ur t-yezzenz ara, ɣas akken mačči d ayla-s yezgaren, s lijaṛa i ten-ikes, ɛeddan-d d yiwen uɛessas mi d-uɣalen s axxam, iseddq-as-t.

Yenna-yas ujenniw-is, ali s ufella n tqubett, yuli, yenna: Atan ay aɛessas, wagi d lmektub-ik, ayen yebɣun yili, anef ad yili! Ulac ataṣ n wussan am assa.

Tameddit yečča imensi s sekksu d bibṛas, acku ur wwiḍen s axxam almi d tikli ad yeɣli yiḍ, ɣef ayen ur tessew ara tmeṭṭut-is ikerciwen d dewwaṛa i d-yuɣ si ssuq.

Yessuli kan učči, yefser iman-is deg usu ad yeṭṭes, ula d ilibuḍen-nni d-yewwi mmi-s seg iqubac ur ten-yeɛriḍ ara ma zgan-as-d, yesred, yeɛya.

Akken isers iɣsan-is, yesla i usiwel n umeẓẓallu-nni i d-yemlal di ṛṛeḥba. Yusa-d akken ad iẓer ma yella ifaq –as d tukarḍa i d-yuker sselɛa-nni si ssuq neɣ ala, acku netta d ameẓẓallu yessnen awal n ṛebbi-s akken yessefk, yugad ad slen at taddart s rredmat-is.

Seg akken ɣur-s asirem ameqqṛan daɣen ulac dacu yezṛa fell-as mraw ( 10 ), yewwi-as-tt-id ansi yeṛɣa lebḥeṛ, yenna-yas: Arraw-ik llah ibarek leɛmeṛ ẓriɣ akk di ddunit ssiɛqat i ten-yecban u yerna ẓriɣ daɣen ur zzmiren ara ad ffɣen akka llan lemmer argaz lɛali n aba-tsen ur yeɣlib ara sputnik deg wenṭag d leqfaza. Seg wass-mi d-cfiɣ i yemma-s n ddunnit, ssawḍeɣ-d axxam-nwen, “ladɣa ya ḥesṛa baba-k ad yeṛḥem ṛebbi iɣsan-is” d axxam n lmumnin u kečč akken i k-ssneɣ mačči d lɛaṣi i telliḍ. Yak teẓriḍ daɣen ula d kečč mebla ma nniɣ-ak kra, mačči d lɣaci i yettagaden medden, yewɛeṛ ma iḥeqqeṛ-ik lğamaɛ, wexxam n ṛebbi.

 

Yerra ad as-yini s temdyazt-is, d lɛib ad slen medden s umeẓẓallu am nekk ffɣeɣ lemdaheb i ṛbeɛṭac, sseṛ-iyi a k-yesseṛ baba ṛebbi! Mraw ( 10 ) ur yeẓri anida tterḍiqen-t, ulac akk ɣur-s isalli n wayen yedṛan di ssuq, maca seg mi i d-as-yenna umeẓẓallu yak teẓriḍ daɣen ula d kečč mebla ma nniɣ-ak kra, yerra-yas tiririt, yennay-as:Ẓriɣ, ẓriɣ a sidi, ɣas kkes anezgum i wul-ik yerna a k-iɛuz ṛebbi ɣef imeslayen-agi n at ṣwab d lḥeṛma!

Amakraḍ-nni yuɣal  s talwit deg ul s axxam-is, mraw ( 10 ) yewwi ti&i&it deg uqeṛṛuy-is teḥma, yekcem s usu. ɣas akken yebred, yeɛya, maca ggummant ad qqnent wallen-is, yesseqdac allaɣ, yettnadi ad yaf ɣef wacu i s-d-yemmeslay umeẓẓallu-amakraḍ. Akken d tiki ad teflali tafat, d lawan ad yali wass, iɣil yufa-d tidett yellan.

Amakraḍ-ameẓẓallu m´akken d as-d-yemmeslay ɣef warraw-is yerna yessegray-as-d awal-nni n yewɛeṛ ma iḥeqqeṛ-ik lğamaɛa, yenna-yas wul-is, ufiɣ-tt-id tura. Yegzi ira a s-yini, kunwi d tawacult igerrzen ladɣa lemmer a tt-rnum taẓallit.

Tigzi yakk d tiḥeṛci dduklent deg allaɣ-is am akken qqaṛen at zik: “ Dduklent Sala d Mala, ṭṭfent abrid ɣer tala”. Yessak-id arraw-is qeccuc, meccuc imiren, wellhen iqeṛṛay-nsen metwal tazuliɣt, bdan taẓallit s ssunna, ẓullen lefjer.

